@qt6636  
I solve this proble by change MXPredGetOutput(out, output_index, &(data[0]), size) to:
`MyPredictor* p = static_cast<MyPredictor*>(pred_hnd);//MyPredictor is the same as MXAPIPredictor in c_predict_api.cc
std::vector<mx_float> data(size);//here size is the length of output from your net
mxnet::NDArray& nd_out = p->out_arrays[output_index];
auto src = nd_out.data();
std::memcpy(&(data[0]), src.dptr_, size * sizeof(mx_float));`
this works for me, and the result is correct.

